    â†’ fam-خ ج‚ل¶  (A , B) Y' fp
    â‰ƒ fam-خ ج‚ل¶  (A , C) Y' (خ ج‚ل¶ -ap-base-fam-base ._â‰ƒ_.fwd fp)
  خ ج‚ل¶ -ap-base-fam-family (i , j)
    = خ -ap-â‰ƒ (خ» a â†’ null-homotopy-postcomp-â‰ƒ (e a) (j a))

  خ ج‚ل¶ -ap-base-fam : خ ج‚ل¶  (A , B) Y' â‰ƒل¶  خ ج‚ل¶  (A , C) Y'
